---
layout: base.njk
title: Web Everything - Home
---

{% from "project-status.njk" import projectStatus %}

<section class="intro">
    <h1>Web Everything</h1>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <strong>Protocol over Implementation.</strong><br>
        Providing the missing standards to bridge the gap between frameworks and enable true interoperability.
    </p>
    <a href="/mission/" style="color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-primary);">
        Read the Manifesto &rarr;
    </a>
</section>

<section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="section-title">Core Standards</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Low-level specifications expanding the capabilities of the platform.</p>
    <div class="project-grid">
        {% for project in projects %}
        {% if project.category == 'standard' %}
        <div class="project-card">
            <a href="/projects/{{ project.id }}/" class="project-card-link" aria-label="View {{ project.name }}"></a>
            <div class="project-header">
                <div class="project-icon">
                    {% if project.isSvg %}
                        <img src="{{ project.icon }}" alt="{{ project.name }} icon" width="48" height="48">
                    {% else %}
                        {{ project.icon }}
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
                <h2 class="project-title">{{ project.name }}</h2>
            </div>
            <p>{{ project.description }}</p>
            <a href="/project-lifecycle/" class="status-link-wrapper">
                {{ projectStatus(project.status) }}
            </a>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Ecosystem & Utilities</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Concrete implementations, polyfills, and developer experience tools.</p>
    <div class="project-grid">
        {% for project in projects %}
        {% if project.category == 'utility' %}
        <div class="project-card">
            <a href="/projects/{{ project.id }}/" class="project-card-link" aria-label="View {{ project.name }}"></a>
            <div class="project-header">
                <div class="project-icon">
                    {% if project.isSvg %}
                        <img src="{{ project.icon }}" alt="{{ project.name }} icon" width="48" height="48">
                    {% else %}
                        {{ project.icon }}
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
                <h2 class="project-title">{{ project.name }}</h2>
            </div>
            <p>{{ project.description }}</p>
            <a href="/project-lifecycle/" class="status-link-wrapper">
                {{ projectStatus(project.status) }}
            </a>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
</section>

<section class="creator-section">
    <h2>About the Creator</h2>
    <p>
        <a href="https://chalbert.github.io/portfolio" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>Nicolas Gilbert</strong></a> is a passionate frontend developer and consultant based in Quebec City, Canada.
        Specializing in modern web applications, Web Components, and developer experience tools.
    </p>
    <div class="creator-links">
        <a href="https://chalbert.github.io/portfolio/contact/" class="creator-link">Work with me</a>
        <a href="https://patreon.com/" class="creator-link">Support this project</a>
    </div>
</section>
